EasyWallet,is,a,bitcoin,storage,system,Users,create,virtual,wallets,to,save,their,bitcoins,The,virtual,wallet,is,accessible,at,a,secret,URL,and,protected,by,a,username,and,password,combination,The,wallets,only,exist,temporarily,if,they,are,not,retrieved,or,visited,at,their,URL,within,a,month,of,its,creation,the,funds,will,return,to,the,original,user,The,EasyWallet,API,is,RESTful,and,allows,users,to,create,new,wallets,initiate,payments,and,view,balances,It,returns,JSON,encoded,data